Kung Fu Tea is my favorite bubble tea franchise.  Everything I've ordered here tends to quench my thirst.  Even items I don't think I'll like turn out to be my new go-to drinks.  I usually order the golden oolong milk tea w bubbles(yes, I know they're not good for me) or the coffee milk tea w bubbles(yes, stop shaking your head at me).  The best thing about this franchise is that the drinks always taste freshly brewed, and you can adjust the iciness and sugar level of all your drinks.  This makes me feel less guilty and happy that I'm not just sipping iced water.  KFT kicks serious butt in the boba arena.
